ale%20of%20the%20Universe%3C%2Fh1%3E%20%3Cp%3EScale%20of%20the%20Universe%20is%20a%20visual%20tool%20for%20getting%20a%20sene%20of%20the%20scale%20of%20various%20objects%20in%20the%20universe.%20It%20has%20a%20wide%20collection%20of%20objects%20ranging%20from%20the%20smallest%20subatomic%20particles%20to%20the%20largest%20galaxies.%20Since%20it's%20initial%20version%20in%202010%20as%20an%20Adobe%20Flash%20app%2C%20it%20has%20since%20been%20updated%20with%20new%20discoveries%20and%20modern%20code.%20Today%2C%20schools%20around%20the%20world%20use%20Scale%20of%20the%20Universe%20as%20a%20learning%20tool%20to%20show%20just%20how%20large%20our%20world%20truly%20is.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch2%20data-svelte-h%3D%22svelte-yae3wl%22%3EMeet%20the%20Creators%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Csection%20class%3D%22developer%20svelte-1v4rj51%22%3E%3Ch3%3ECary%20Huang%3C%2Fh3%3E%20%3Cp%20class%3D%22svelte-1v4rj51%22%3E%3Ci%3EOriginal%20Creator%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%20class%3D%22svelte-1v4rj51%22%3ECary%20Huang%20is%20the%20original%20creator%20of%20Scale%20of%20the%20Universe%20from%20over%2010%20years%20ago.%20Along%20with%20his%20brother%2C%20He%20created%20%3Ca%20href%3D%22https%3A%2F%2Fyoutube.com%2Fjacknjellify%22%3EJacknJellify%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20YouTube%20channel%20that%20produces%20animations%20for%20kids%20which%20has%20reached%20over%20a%20billion%20views%20and%20a%20million%20subscribers.%20His%20personal%20YouTube%20channel%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%22https%3A%2F%2Fyoutube.com%2Fcarykh%22%3Ecarykh%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20has%20evolved%20to%20educate%20and%20entertain%20viewers%20about%20machine%20learning%2C%20science%2C%20maths%2C%20and%20programming.%20In%202020%20Cary%20graduated%20from%20Stanford%20University%20with%20a%20degree%20in%20computer%20science.%20He%20loves%20to%20solve%20Rubiks%20Cubes%20and%20is%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%22https%3A%2F%2Fen.wiktionary.org%2Fwiki%2Fumbraphile%22%3Eumbraphile%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%20class%3D%22developer%20svelte-1v4rj51%22%3E%3Ch3%3EPeter%20Ruette%3C%2Fh3%3E%20%3Cp%20class%3D%22svelte-1v4rj51%22%3E%3Ci%3EProject%20Manager%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%20class%3D%22svelte-1v4rj51%22%3EPeter%20Ruette%20is%20the%20project%20manager%20for%20Scale%20of%20the%20Universe%20and%20a%20close%20friend%20of%20Cary.%20Peter%20has%20experience%20in%20business%20management%20and%20marketing%20in%20and%20beyond%20software%20development%20for%20both%20startups%20as%20well%20as%20major%20companies.%20Currently%2C%20he%20is%20working%20with%20the%20startup%20%3Ca%20href%3D%22https%3A%2F%2Fneurosnap.ai%22%3Eneurosnap.ai%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Peter%20is%20interested%20in%20expanding%20the%20educational%20opportunities%20of%20Scale%20of%20the%20Universe%20and%20has%20connections%20with%20teachers%20and%20schools%20around%20the%20world%20who%20enjoy%20using%20SOTU%20to%20teach%20their%20students%20about%20the%20diversity%20of%20the%20universe%20across%20time%20and%20space.%20Peter%20has%20visited%20countries%20including%20(but%20certainly%20not%20limited%20to)%20Indonesia%2C%20Zimbabwe%2C%20Brazil%2C%20and%20France%20where%20he%20has%20gained%20firsthand%20experience%20with%20the%20cultures%20of%20these%20areas.%20Peter's%20hobbies%20include%20hiking%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%22https%3A%2F%2Fgenerals.io%22%3Egenerals.io%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20Pokemon%20Go.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%20class%3D%22developer%20svelte-1v4rj51%22%3E%3Ch3%3EChloe%20Caruso%3C%2Fh3%3E%20%3Cp%20class%3D%22svelte-1v4rj51%22%3E%3Ci%3EDeveloper%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%20class%3D%22svelte-1v4rj51%22%3EChloe%20Caruso%20is%20one%20of%20the%20developers%20behind%20the%20Scale%20of%20the%20Universe%20website.%20In%20the%20past%2C%20she's%20worked%20on%20other%20projects%20such%20as%20Elemental%204%2C%20a%20game%20that%20had%20millions%20of%20players%20with%2014%2C000%20submissions%20of%20user-created%20content%2C%20and%20participated%20in%20many%20game%20jams.%20Today%2C%20she%20works%20professionally%20as%20a%20software%20engineer%2C%20spending%20free%20time%20producing%20music%20and%20videos.%20All%20of%20her%20work%20is%20available%20to%20admire%20at%20%3Ca%20href%3D%22https%3A%2F%2Fpaperclover.net%22%3Epaperclover.net%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%20class%3D%22developer%20svelte-1v4rj51%22%3E%3Ch3%3EBen%20Plate%3C%2Fh3%3E%20%3Cp%20class%3D%22svelte-1v4rj51%22%3E%3Ci%3EDeveloper%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%20class%3D%22svelte-1v4rj51%22%3EBen%20Plate%20is%20a%20developer%20for%20Scale%20of%20Universe%20with%20a%20decade%20of%20programming%20experience.%20In%20the%20past%2C%20he%20worked%20with%20a%20professor%20at%20Arizona%20State%20University%20to%20create%20a%20deep%20neural%20network%20that%20generates%20novel%20music%20by%20training%20off%20of%20the%20works%20of%20classical%20composers.%20Now%2C%20he's%20studying%20computer%20science%20at%20UC%20Berkeley%20and%20is%20the%20lead%20developer%20behind%20the%20new%2C%20unreleased%20website%20at%20%3Ca%20href%3D%22https%3A%2F%2Focf.io%22%3Ethe%20OCF%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20student-run%20organization%20at%20UC%20Berkeley%20that%20provides%20free%20computing%20resources%20to%20students%20and%20faculty%2C%20as%20well%20as%20the%20lead%20developer%20behind%20Moonband%2C%20a%20device%20that%20helps%20prevent%20drowning%20that%20received%202nd%20place%20in%20the%20Johns%20Hopkins%20Global%20Healthcare%20Design%20Competition.%20On%20his%20offtime%2C%20Ben%20enjoys%20playing%20chess%2C%20grand%20strategy%20games%2C%20Catan%2C%20and%20table%20tennis.%20You%20can%20learn%20more%20about%20him%20at%20his%20website%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%22https%3A%2F%2Fben9583.com%22%3Eben9583.com%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%20class%3D%22developer%20svelte-1v4rj51%22%3E%3Ch3%3EJames%20o'Loughlin%3C%2Fh3%3E%20%3Cp%20class%3D%22svelte-1v4rj51%22%3E%3Ci%3ESEO%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%20class%3D%22svelte-1v4rj51%22%3EJames%20o%E2%80%99Loughlin%20is%20an%20SEO%20specialist%20for%20Scale%20of%20the%20Universe.%20He%20is%20a%20professor%20and%20is%20the%20CEO%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pixaura.com%2F%22%3EPixaura%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20digital%20marketing%20company%20that%20specializes%20in%20design%20and%20SEO.%20In%202011%2C%20he%20started%20mining%20Bitcoin%20and%20years%20later%20he%20was%20able%20to%20pay%20off%20his%20house%20using%20the%20profits.%20Currently%20he's%20also%20working%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cliqrex.com%2F%22%3ECliqRex%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20an%20app%20that%20allows%20users%20to%20provide%20recommendations%20on%20books%2C%20movies%2C%20shows%2C%20and%20more%20to%20friends%20and%20uses%20algorithms%20to%20determine%20what%20people%20have%20similar%20'affinities'%20and%20provide%20recommendations%20based%20off%20of%20their%20mutual%20scores.%20In%20his%20freetime%2C%20James%20likes%20to%20bike%20and%20has%20a%20group%20he%20leads%20among%20friends.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3C%2Fsection%3E%3C%2Fmain%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%22footer%20svelte-oyjo2h%22%20style%3D%22%22%3E%3Cdiv%20style%3D%22display%3Aflex%3Bwidth%3A100%25%3Bheight%3A90px%3Bflex-direction%3Acolumn%3Balign-items%3Acenter%22%3E%3Cins%20class%3D%22adsbygoogle%20responsive-ad%20svelte-oyjo2h%22%20style%3D%22display%3Ablock%3Bheight%3A90px%3Bmargin%3A0%20auto%22%20data-ad-client%3D%22ca-pub-7698832499306881%22%20data-ad-slot%3D%221598105164%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%20%3Cfooter%20class%3D%22svelte-oyjo2h%22%3E%C2%A9%202026%20Scale%20of%20Universe.%20All%20rights%20reserved.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%22mailto%3Aadmin%40scaleofuniverse.com%22%20target%3D%22_blank%22%3EContact%20us%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Ffooter%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%20id%3D%22svelte-announcer%22%20aria-live%3D%22assertive%22%20aria-atomic%3D%22true%22%20style%3D%22position%3A%20absolute%3B%20left%3A%200px%3B%20top%3A%200px%3B%20clip%3A%20rect(0px%2C%200px%2C%200px%2C%200px)%3B%20clip-path%3A%20inset(50%25)%3B%20overflow%3A%20hidden%3B%20white-space%3A%20nowrap%3B%20width%3A%201px%3B%20height%3A%201px%3B%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%0A%20%20%0A%0A%0A%3C%2Fbody%3E%0A%3C%2F